{"tid":665943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"在港外國人：不明白為何廣東話不是港人母語","createTime":"2018-05-15T12:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T15:56:56.000Z","uid":51271,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b221507a629f0f05adb5c5275d2e20d0865a0619","tid":665943,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T12:07:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1396499-20180515.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1396499-20180515.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=cppOGrXEjPmccJsJqcfD7pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=5fb30df0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1396499-20180515.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=99616e89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1396499-20180515.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近日教育局一篇教材引起社會爭論，廣東話是否香港人的母語。有在香港讀書和工作的外國人表示，不明白為何廣東話不是港人母語，他們為了在香港生活，都努力學習廣東話。<br />\n<br />\n來自非洲迦納的Obed來港修讀碩士，學習廣東話的原因，除了想在香港找工作，亦是為了尊重香港人。他又說，希望靠廣東話在香港覓得女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n來了香港數年的日本人藤本真由美，最喜歡香港的潮語，例如「射波」、「唔使急，最緊要快」。藤本指香港是國際城市，每天可以接觸到來自世界各地的語言，但最多人說的便是廣東話。她對於「廣東話不是香港人母語」的說法感到奇怪，\b即使自己不是香港人，也認為要支持保存廣東話。"},{"pid":"c4b7816300680458e9cf2c2f774db6190d5b7065","tid":665943,"uid":36964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T12:08:29.000Z","msg":"Because CCP."},{"pid":"16e16859c86832f80561ed18b4420856ef39983f","tid":665943,"uid":23170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T12:46:30.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a325930e82ba04641b1799a6c1542faefbcddc","tid":665943,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T12:47:54.000Z","msg":"自己母語係咩條友講出黎條友其實係咪戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30ed7692cae0eb598aa2dcd3daf60e42ef0db3f","tid":665943,"uid":21899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T12:50:14.000Z","msg":"rthk高汁"},{"pid":"503072e568b22bc77e3d68145b699a9c0f6b0142","tid":665943,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T12:58:21.000Z","msg":"因為香港係中國架囉咁簡單"},{"pid":"ca4e340846595ecaa496c034da4721a857ec76bf","tid":665943,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6026cce9bad4bf503c1d6807ae41a77a0f75e24a","tid":665943,"uid":56954,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"503072e568b22bc77e3d68145b699a9c0f6b0142","tid":665943,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T12:58:21.000Z","msg":"因為香港係中國架囉咁簡單"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:27:39.000Z","msg":"錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己人點會咁一定係比外人搞<br />\n香港係中國殖民地"},{"pid":"89d013a0c764e200153d57c5ca3c69998737246f","tid":665943,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:32:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd9a7ffa74828e38b88a605e2397a6dc82e34889","tid":665943,"uid":38904,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"89d013a0c764e200153d57c5ca3c69998737246f","tid":665943,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:32:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T14:38:47.000Z","msg":"係都你隻五毛狗走先"},{"pid":"3123f81c5017915a48aaaea24ed91a0e29801c52","tid":665943,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:27:23.000Z","msg":"我都唔明呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2d0549853021ac8ae7e87680e7d9eafd33cb71","tid":665943,"uid":133751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:34:44.000Z","msg":"根本上去拗廣東話是否港人母語呢樣野已經on9"},{"pid":"b4b850a187a2454f11932050e546b3c5c01acca2",